    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300470/extras/4fd58c1e28ef81f683fcd0b290bc58f8.poster.avif?t=1770389760\" width=600 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300470/extras/4fd58c1e28ef81f683fcd0b290bc58f8.webm?t=1770389760\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300470/extras/4fd58c1e28ef81f683fcd0b290bc58f8.mp4?t=1770389760\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>We are rats circling the ruins of great civilizations. All we have are our songs and the dream that they will not fade away too soon.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300470/extras/0fbed0789ababf9e306be3f0c92ef81f.webp?t=1770389760\" width=301 height=6 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300470/extras/f66613116290e524068b12a03bac0001.poster.avif?t=1770389760\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300470/extras/f66613116290e524068b12a03bac0001.webm?t=1770389760\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300470/extras/f66613116290e524068b12a03bac0001.mp4?t=1770389760\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Songs of Rats is a dark indie RPG inspired by choose-your-own-adventure books. Create your hero, enter the ever-changing maze, fight for survival, and uncover hidden mysteries. Choose your path wisely, upgrade your gear, find companions, and discover the truth behind the reality that surrounds you.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Wreckage is an ever-changing labyrinth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Those who live here stick to their burrows, settlements, and hideouts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But there are madmen who abandon safety to venture into the unknown.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Madmen like you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300470/extras/0fbed0789ababf9e306be3f0c92ef81f.webp?t=1770389760\" width=301 height=6 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300470/extras/65b9a96df7b24ecc9c45f1677e8a8745.poster.avif?t=1770389760\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300470/extras/65b9a96df7b24ecc9c45f1677e8a8745.webm?t=1770389760\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300470/extras/65b9a96df7b24ecc9c45f1677e8a8745.mp4?t=1770389760\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Songs of Rats is a roguelike RPG in which you will delve into a mysterious Wreckland filled with secrets of long-gone civilizations.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Develop your character and gather a team</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face the changing world and its challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the dark secrets of fallen civilizations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face strange, human and inhuman enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SURVIVE!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pet your faithful dog!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fight for your life!</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Face real nightmares!</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Find or lose all your hope!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300470/extras/0fbed0789ababf9e306be3f0c92ef81f.webp?t=1770389760\" width=301 height=6 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300470/extras/423cc4d0c1e67d71940adf4e69fc303c.poster.avif?t=1770389760\" width=600 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300470/extras/423cc4d0c1e67d71940adf4e69fc303c.webm?t=1770389760\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300470/extras/423cc4d0c1e67d71940adf4e69fc303c.mp4?t=1770389760\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
